Reasoning: The paper deals with online learning, which is a subfield of machine learning and falls under the category of cs.LG (Machine Learning). The use of sufficient statistics and the Burkholder method suggests that the paper may also be relevant to information theory (cs.IT) and data structures (cs.DS). The development of a novel online strategy for matrix prediction and linear-time/space prediction strategy for supervised learning suggests that the paper may also be relevant to artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and statistics (cs.ST).
